description: Product Description Product Features Soft Chew Squeaky Sound No Stuffing Cotton Easy to Wipe Clean No Stuffing Octopus Squeaky Dog Toy Interactive and Fetch Play for Dogs Octopus squeaky toys are made of safe and premium plush polyester fibers, and there is no filling inside, so there is no need to worry about dogs swallowing or suffocating while playing.
